{"heading":"Come and drink; salvation is free—The Lord will make an everlasting covenant with Israel—Seek the Lord while He is near.","number":55,"verseCount":13,"verses":[[1,["Ho, every one that ",["thirsteth",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 42:2 (1–3)","ot/ps/42.2"],"; ",["143:6 (5–12)","ot/ps/143.6"],"; ",["Luke 6:21","nt/luke/6.21"],"; ",["John 4:14 (13–15)","nt/john/4.14"],"; ",["7:37 (37–39)","nt/john/7.37"],"; ",["2 Ne. 9:50 (50–51)","bofm/2-ne/9.50"],"."]]],", come ye to the ",["waters",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Living Water","tg/living-water"],"."]]],", and he that hath no money; come ye, buy, and eat; yea, come, ",["buy",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Ne. 26:25","bofm/2-ne/26.25"],"."]]]," wine and milk without money and without ",["price",["study-note-ref","d",[["Matt. 10:8","nt/matt/10.8"],"."]]],"."]],[2,["Wherefore do ye ",["spend",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Waste","tg/waste"],"."]]]," money for ",["that which is",["clarity-word"]]," not bread? and your ",["labour",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Labor","tg/labor"],"."]]]," for ",["that which",["clarity-word"]]," satisfieth not? hearken ",["diligently",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Diligence","tg/diligence"],"."]]]," unto me, and eat ye ",["that which is",["clarity-word"]]," good, and let your soul delight itself in fatness."]],[3,["Incline your ear, and ",["come",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 11:28 (28–30)","nt/matt/11.28"],"; ",["John 6:44","nt/john/6.44"],"; ",["Heb. 7:25","nt/heb/7.25"],"; ",["3 Ne. 12:20 (19–20)","bofm/3-ne/12.20"],"; ",["D&C 45:46 (45–46)","dc-testament/dc/45.46"],"; ",["132:12","dc-testament/dc/132.12"],"."]]]," unto me: hear, and your ",["soul",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Soul","tg/soul"],"."]]]," shall live; and I will make an everlasting ",["covenant",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG New and Everlasting Covenant","tg/new-and-everlasting-covenant"],"."]]]," with you, ",["even",["clarity-word"]]," the ",["sure",["study-note-ref","d",[["Acts 13:34 (26–41)","nt/acts/13.34"],"."]]]," mercies of