-ref","c",[["Prov. 14:12","ot/prov/14.12"],"."]]]," my ",["ways",["study-note-ref","d",[["Jacob 4:8","bofm/jacob/4.8"],"."]]],", saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],"."]],[9,["For ",["as",["clarity-word"]]," the heavens are higher than the earth, so are my ",["ways",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Spirituality","tg/spirituality"],"."]]]," ",["higher",["study-note-ref","b",[["Job 33:12","ot/job/33.12"],"; ",["Abr. 3:19","pgp/abr/3.19"],"."]]]," than your ways, and my ",["thoughts",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ps. 139:17 (17–24)","ot/ps/139.17"],"."]]]," than your thoughts."]],[10,["For as the ",["rain",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Nature, Earth","tg/nature-earth"],"."]]]," cometh down, and the snow from heaven, and returneth not thither, but watereth the earth, and maketh it bring forth and bud, that it may give seed to the sower, and ",["bread",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Bread","tg/bread"],"."]]]," to the eater:"]],[11,["So shall my ",["word",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 32:2","ot/deut/32.2"],"; ",["Ezek. 12:25","ot/ezek/12.25"],"; ",["D&C 121:45","dc-testament/dc/121.45"],"."]]]," be that goeth forth out of my mouth: it shall not return unto me void, but it shall accomplish that which I please, and it shall prosper ",["in the thing",["clarity-word"]]," whereto I sent it."]],[12,["For ye shall go out with ",["joy",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]],", and be led forth with peace: the mountains and the hills shall break forth before you into singing, and all the ",["trees",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Chr. 16:33 (31–33)","ot/1-chr/16.33"],"; ",["D&C 128:23 (22–23)","dc-testament/dc/128.23"],"."]]]," of the field shall clap ",["their",["clarity-word"]]," hands."]],[13,["Instead of the thorn shall come up the ",["fir tree",["study-note-ref","a",["HEB cypress tree. ",["TG Earth, Renewal of","tg/earth-renewal-of"],"."]]],", and instead of the brier shall come up the myrtle tree: and it shall be to the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," f